g.text: (Amir tells me there are no CDs in the future so)

g.text: Maybe the rat's an On-lyne fan too

g.text: Haha I actually think they do. Not sure they could carry a CD in their little paws though.

g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j1911337018
g.text: I actually think it's cool how you see past the surface of pop music.

g.text: Look, we aren't all going to like the same things.

g.text: I don't think Zeke would approve of stealing. (No, I didn't take it. Lol.)

g.text: There are no CD players either, so even if I had it, I wouldn't be able to do much with it.

g.text: Oh... Well, metal makes a big comeback in the future

g.text: That's too bad. I'm out of ideas.

g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j150877548

g.text: Well, good luck with your search.

g.title: j2065018595
g.text: then I will dominate the future!

g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j2074808237
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j289472540

g.title: j3844886677

g.title: j3638300032
g.text: hope u have a good day ^_^

g.text: well, nobody comes after punk songs for being three power chords, u know?

g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.text: like sure, thrash out three chords and shout about making out with 10 blondes in a night. that's sooo cool. ur sooo real

g.text: I just mean you should like whatever you like. Screw what everyone else thinks.

g.title: j2025890830

g.text: Neither is better. They're just different flavors.
